   <section id="search">
    <title>Search</title>
    <para>The search field allows you to find items in different categories. Type
    in at least three consecutive characters (the underline character will act
    as a wildcard-char) and depending on the context you will
    be prompted with a result list containing items of following catgories:</para>
    <itemizedlist>
     <listitem>
      <para>Company / Customers</para>
     </listitem>
     <listitem>
      <para>Milestones</para>
     </listitem>
     <listitem>
      <para>People</para>
     </listitem>
     <listitem>
      <para>Projects</para>
     </listitem>
     <listitem>
      <para>Resources</para>
     </listitem>
     <listitem>
      <para>Tasks</para>
     </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
    <para>After selection you will be led to the items detail page.</para>
   </section>
